room_description: Dr. Hubert is a biomedical engineer at Mississippi State University. You have broken into his lab because you've heard rumors that he has created an airborne virus to create mutations and he plans to release it somewhere in town. You know that Dr. Hubert must have developed an antidote for the virus so he can protect himself from infection. You need to find the antidote to save yourself and the rest of the community, but you have to act quick because he's only on lunch for 60 minutes.
